betterquesting:10.desc:8:
§7§oThis gate has two outputs, a setting input, and a lock input.

The outputs have the taller torches.

The setting input has the shorter torch.

The lock input has just redstone.

When the lock input receives a redstone signal, the output replicates what the setting input indefintely, even after it changes.

If the setting is on, pulsing the lock turns the output on.

If the setting is off, pulsing the lock turns the output off.
